		We succeeded in developing our MVP (designs shown below) within our one month deadline. The <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.duxilio.sock" target="_blank" class="underline">Android app</a> was less successful because of the market saturation within the Google Play Store. The <a href="https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/sock-securely-store-images/id1447546532" target="_blank" class="underline">App Store</a> was more successful with over 4000 App Store impressions within just a couple of days. When the app was finished we needed some funding for our next set of features and that's when we started our next project: <a href="/work/donny" class="underline">donny.fund</a>.
	</p>
